  "texts": [
    "PadChest [357] and CheXpert [358] also comprise chest X-ray images and corresponding medical reports, enriching the variety and quantity of chest X-ray images.",
    "For pathology imaging, OpenPath [255] is sourced from Twitter's medical knowledge-sharing platform, containing more than 200K pathology images with descriptions by medical professionals.",
    "PathVQA [360] is a pathology VQA dataset, which includes 4,998 images and 32,799 QA pairs.",
    "Quilt-1M [368] is a large histopathology dataset, which consists of 1M image-text pairs.",
    "PatchGastricADC22 [361] includes 262,777 image patches extracted from 991 WSIs with the relevant diagnostic captions."
  ],
